            "urn": 1602900,
            "body": "<p>Abu Mas'ud Al-Badri (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: The Prophet (\ufdfa) said, \"When someone spends on his family seeking his reward for it from Allah, it is counted as a charity from him\".<br/><br/><b>[Al-Bukhari and Muslim]</b>.<br/><br/></p>",
